column5: Hey guys  Gonna be in Goderich for the long weekend and I will be bringing the boat. I know there are lots of bass in the maitland , but how is the fishing in the near by harbour or the lake???  Are there any perch or walleye near by this time of year???  Thanks for any help guys !!
My cousin who practices his mine resue diving in the harbour has seen everything there from Musky to Walleye just not numbers of fish.
